    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 103.</p><p>Tier II: Untarnished Blood</p><p>Prerequisite: Iron Stance</p><p>Cleanse Effect. You can use 1 LP at the start of your turn to end all conditions or harmful effects not created by mythical techniques or spells of 8th level or higher currently afflicting you.</p><p>Greater Health. Your hit point maximum cannot be reduced in any way, and you are immune to spells and effects that would immediately reduce your hit points to 0 or kill you outright.</p></div>",
